00:24:12.500 --> 00:24:13.680
Are you roasting me?

00:24:16.200 --> 00:24:17.200
I know...

00:24:17.440 --> 00:24:19.040
I know I've been

00:24:19.640 --> 00:24:22.280
working so hard that
my face is all run-down.

00:24:22.880 --> 00:24:23.760
Right?

00:24:24.360 --> 00:24:25.880
Yet your face seems
as young as ever.

00:24:26.680 --> 00:24:27.760
That's right.

00:24:29.080 --> 00:24:30.280
Because you

00:24:31.110 --> 00:24:32.480
take everything too seriously.

00:24:33.260 --> 00:24:34.640
You should relax once in a while.

00:24:38.350 --> 00:24:40.080
It's impossible to for me

00:24:40.180 --> 00:24:42.840
to be completely relaxed, Alex.

00:24:44.430 --> 00:24:46.780
You know what my
career's responsibilities were

00:24:46.810 --> 00:24:48.360
and what I had to do.

00:24:49.290 --> 00:24:50.400
I'm well aware

00:24:50.810 --> 00:24:52.160
and understand.

00:24:54.570 --> 00:24:56.760
But haven't things
been better than before?

00:25:13.790 --> 00:25:15.240
Please don't put pressure on me.

00:25:22.360 --> 00:25:23.290
Nil.

00:25:26.610 --> 00:25:28.600
Am I making you uncomfortable?

00:25:30.840 --> 00:25:32.370
I wouldn't say that.

00:25:33.790 --> 00:25:35.000
Then what is it?

00:25:36.160 --> 00:25:38.400
What made you put up a wall
between us

00:25:39.830 --> 00:25:41.360
or was it just an excuse?

00:25:42.950 --> 00:25:44.440
If you don't want to be with me,

00:25:44.900 --> 00:25:46.240
you can be honest with me.

00:25:52.760 --> 00:25:54.780
I don't...

00:25:56.520 --> 00:25:58.440
I don't think I can give
you answers at this time.

00:26:00.910 --> 00:26:02.160
Listen to me, Nil.

00:26:03.280 --> 00:26:05.400
I'm mature enough to
understand everything.

00:26:06.410 --> 00:26:08.320
Just say the word that
you want me to wait

00:26:08.810 --> 00:26:10.280
and I'll always wait for you.

00:26:10.320 --> 00:26:13.800
You know, I would
never ask you to do that.

00:26:17.580 --> 00:26:20.000
Does this mean I have to
keep waiting for you to answer

00:26:21.290 --> 00:26:23.200
without a destination like this?

00:26:37.360 --> 00:26:38.560
You don't have to wait.

00:26:46.570 --> 00:26:47.710
If you meet someone new,

00:26:47.740 --> 00:26:50.240
have new ambitions, then I...

