Given what you've said...

00:27:17.720 --> 00:27:19.600
I really have to
let you go, huh?

00:27:33.700 --> 00:27:34.880
Thank you, Nil.

00:27:38.320 --> 00:27:40.080
Thanks for everything.

00:27:51.010 --> 00:27:52.480
But I wanted to let you know that

00:27:55.860 --> 00:27:57.600
I will always be
waiting for you here.

00:28:00.390 --> 00:28:01.920
Someday, when you're ready

00:28:02.800 --> 00:28:04.000
and open up your heart,

00:28:07.440 --> 00:28:08.880
remember that I'll be here.

00:28:25.600 --> 00:28:26.520
Thank you.

00:28:43.030 --> 00:28:44.720
What are you doing
standing here all by yourself?

00:28:47.130 --> 00:28:48.440
Something on your
mind about Alan?

00:28:51.230 --> 00:28:52.840
Would you take me for a walk?

00:28:57.800 --> 00:28:59.080
Go for a walk?

00:28:59.570 --> 00:29:00.960
