You're coming to stay
at my place to night.

00:29:10.390 --> 00:29:11.480
Being alone

00:29:11.860 --> 00:29:13.150
might get you lost
in your thoughts.

00:29:13.400 --> 00:29:14.120
Also,

00:29:14.140 --> 00:29:16.960
traveling back and forth to the
hospital is a waste of money.

00:29:18.070 --> 00:29:19.040
Another thing,

00:29:19.350 --> 00:29:20.800
if you don't get enough sleep,

00:29:21.280 --> 00:29:22.960
you'll slack off at work again.

00:29:24.370 --> 00:29:25.640
Why'd you suddenly invite
me to stay at your place?

00:29:25.750 --> 00:29:27.440
Are you planning something?

00:29:29.350 --> 00:29:30.600
What plan?

00:29:31.760 --> 00:29:32.600
Why?

00:29:33.810 --> 00:29:35.200
You can't have a sleepover?

00:29:37.570 --> 00:29:39.160
I thought you said
we're boyfriends now.

00:29:40.300 --> 00:29:41.160
Wait...

00:29:41.330 --> 00:29:43.080
When did I become your boyfriend?

00:29:43.940 --> 00:29:45.360
Let's see...

00:29:47.560 --> 00:29:48.560
Oh!

00:29:49.140 --> 00:29:50.480
I remembered.

00:29:51.740 --> 00:29:52.760
You're right,

00:29:53.730 --> 00:29:54.760
Honey.

