about what's to come

00:34:48.219 --> 00:34:49.600
is a good thing,

00:34:50.400 --> 00:34:53.360
but if it makes the
present moment unhappy,

00:34:55.030 --> 00:34:56.280
I think it's better to just let go.

00:34:59.430 --> 00:35:00.560
