00:35:03.120 --> 00:35:04.960
Let me take care of
my work real quick.

00:35:07.330 --> 00:35:08.240
Alright.

00:35:41.760 --> 00:35:42.960
Now go take a shower.

00:35:44.870 --> 00:35:46.360
After I've showered,

00:35:46.670 --> 00:35:47.840
promise that

00:35:48.560 --> 00:35:49.880
you'll reward me, okay?

00:35:52.720 --> 00:35:53.650
Go.

00:35:54.280 --> 00:35:55.520
Fine.

00:36:14.220 --> 00:36:15.220
Here you go, Win.

00:36:15.330 --> 00:36:16.640
Your favorite.

00:36:16.950 --> 00:36:18.320
So you don't ever have to

00:36:18.950 --> 00:36:20.320
go out to get one again.

00:36:23.400 --> 00:36:25.200
I'm here to visit
you, as promised.

00:36:27.460 --> 00:36:28.840
Thank you

00:36:29.750 --> 00:36:31.680
for carrying out the promise
throughout your whole life.

00:36:35.100 --> 00:36:36.680
You've never abandoned me...

00:36:37.540 --> 00:36:38.800
Follow me, quick.

00:36:40.870 --> 00:36:44.200
regardless of the
circumstances we're in.

00:36:45.410 --> 00:36:46.920
I love you so much, Win.

00:36:48.040 --> 00:36:49.360
From now on,

00:36:50.620 --> 00:36:51.560
there won't ever be

00:36:51.590 --> 00:36:53.720
a hospital for the
forgotten anymore.

00:36:59.390 --> 00:37:00.360
Win...

00:37:01.170 --> 00:37:03.360
You'll live on in
my memory forever.

00:37:07.250 --> 00:37:08.560
You remember

00:37:09.440 --> 00:37:11.560
when you told me

00:37:12.490 --> 00:37:14.920
you wanted to see me
live a happy life every day?

00:37:20.280 --> 00:37:21.560
I've been happy

00:37:22.160 --> 00:37:23.840
every day, just like
you wanted me to.

00:37:30.250 --> 00:37:32.640
You will be a part
of my life forever.

